                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Secretary of State to the Minister in Ecuador</hi>
                        (<persName corresp="#p_HCS1">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hartman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <dateline>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<placeName>
                        <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-11-14T19:00:00-05:00">
                        <hi rend="italic">November 14, 1914, 7 p.m.</hi>
                    </date>
                </dateline>
                <p rend="center">[Telegram]</p>
                <p>British and French Governments complain that the neutrality proclamation made by
                    the Ecuadorian Government is not being enforced. Charge is made of the use of
                    the Galápagos Islands as a naval base by the Germans. Discreetly inquire as to
                    the facts.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_BWJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">W. J. Bryan</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
